<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><key>Db</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Jesuh kong kha khua-zakip ah, Thanter u, Thawngtha bia cu, Misual kha
 khamhnak chim hna u, Ceunak kha karh chin ko seh.

[C1]
   Thawngtha bia (Thawngtha bia) vawlei cung khua zakip ah (zakip ah)
   Thanter tuah u, Jesuh thawng kha thanter tuah u, A min zungzal thangthat
   u.

[V2]
 Thawngtha bia chim tu thlah hna u, Ceunak kha kalpi hna seh,
 Sual-muihnak ramchung mi hna nih, Ceunak kha an hmuh hlan tiang.

[C2]
   Thawngtha bia (Thawngtha bia) vawlei cung khua zakip ah (zakip ah)
   Thanter tuah u, Jesuh thawng kha thanter tuah u, A min zungzal thangthat
   u.

[V3]
 Lawmhnak thawng kha kan thanter lai, Fing le tlang khua zakip ah,
 Jesuh kong kha kan chimh hna lai. Dawtnak le khamhnak kong kha.

[C3]
   Thawngtha bia (Thawngtha bia) vawlei cung khua zakip ah (zakip ah)
   Thanter tuah u, Jesuh thawng kha thanter tuah u, A min zungzal thangthat
   u.

[V4]
 Ramdang ca thla kan cam lioah, Kan ram kha philh hlah u sih; Jesuh
 Khrih kan Siangpahrang cu, Kan ram ah hin Bawi cang seh.

[C4]
   Thawngtha bia (Thawngtha bia) vawlei cung khua zakip ah (zakip ah)
   Thanter tuah u, Jesuh thawng kha thanter tuah u, A min zungzal thangthat
   u.</lyrics>
<title>KHUAZAKIP AH THANTER U CH409</title>
<hymn_number>409</hymn_number>
</song>